'''''That's Christmas to Me''''' 是無伴奏組合[[Pentatonix|Pentatonix]]第三張錄音室專輯，亦是繼''[[PTXmas|PTXmas]]''後第二張聖誕專輯。除了曾收錄於''[[PTX,_Vols._1&2|PTX, Vols. 1&2]]''日本版的[[冰心鎖|Let It Go]]外，全碟均為未曾發行的歌曲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6214079/pentatonix-sets-vol-3-release-date-second-holiday-album?utm_source=twitter|title=Pentatonix Sets 'Vol. 3' Release Date, Second Holiday Album|date=8 August 2014|work=Billboard|accessdate=6 October 2014|archive-date=2014-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140920052803/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6214079/pentatonix-sets-vol-3-release-date-second-holiday-album?utm_source=twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref>

專輯於2014年10月21日由[[RCA_Records|RCA Records]]發行<ref name = allmusic>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/thats-christmas-to-me-mw0002745911|title=That's Christmas to Me - Pentatonix - Songs, Reviews, Credits, Awards - AllMusic|work=AllMusic|accessdate=6 October 2014|archive-date=2014-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017032933/http://www.allmusic.com/album/thats-christmas-to-me-mw0002745911|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以碟內唯一一首原創歌曲命名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://newsok.com/video-pentatonix-releases-ep-ptx-vol.-3-today/article/5344810|title=Video: Pentatonix releases EP “PTX Vol. 3|work=NewsOK.com|accessdate=6 October 2014|archive-date=2014-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009162444/http://newsok.com/video-pentatonix-releases-ep-ptx-vol.-3-today/article/5344810|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.axs.com/the-sing-off-champs-pentatonix-bringing-a-cappella-into-the-mainstream-16699|title='The Sing-Off' champs Pentatonix bringing a cappella into the mainstream|work=AXS|accessdate=6 October 2014|archive-date=2014-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010040605/http://www.axs.com/the-sing-off-champs-pentatonix-bringing-a-cappella-into-the-mainstream-16699|dead-url=no}}</ref>

